Helper scripts to build the speech-dispatcher-voxin package.

Example: packages for Fedora 25

* build the i686 package under VM1 (Fedora 32 bits)
cd speech-dispatcher-voxin
./build.sh

# the build.i686 directory contains the i686 package

* build the x86_64 package under VM2 (e.g. Fedora 64 bits)
cd speech-dispatcher-voxin
./build.sh

# the build.x86_64 directory contains the x86_64 package

* copy the packages to the voxin installer
DISTRIB_RELEASE=25
rm $VOXIN_INSTALLER/packages/fedora.$DISTRIB_RELEASE/speech-dispatcher-voxin*
cp build.{i686,x86_64}/*rpm $VOXIN_INSTALLER/packages/fedora.$DISTRIB_RELEASE
